=Description=

"GPT is a web program that helps coordinating a grassroot volunteer campaign based on the act of contacting political candidates before an election.  Its aim is to act as a contact directory and to gather all information regarding the work of a decentralized volunteer campaign (who is in charge of which candidate or constituency, etc.).  GPT also helps maintaining a numbering of candidates supports."


